{"tid":2394673,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"AAPL 2020 Q4 財報分析","createTime":"2021-02-04T10:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T12:10:00.000Z","uid":365423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e3aa8710544ded6d18b13863c9391e3b625835b2","tid":2394673,"uid":365423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"在 2020 Q4首次突破千億美元營收，達1114.4億美元，YoY成長21.37%。毛利443.3 億美元，YoY成長25.9%，毛利率39.8%，為去年四季新高。營業利益為 335.3 億美元，YoY成長 31.15%，而營業利潤率30% ，比去年同期上升了一成，意味蘋果隨著營收的成長，也取得了更好的營運獲利能力。淨利287.6 億，YoY 成長 29.31%，EPS  1.68 美元。<br />\n<br />\n營收成長率是 21.37%，扣除成本的毛利成長率是 25.9%，扣除營業費用的營業利潤成長率是 31.15%，後者比前者高，代表營收成長同時獲利能力和營運亦有提升。<br />\n<br />\n各地區營收成長率： 北美 12%、歐洲 17.3%、中國 57%、日本 33.1%，亞太其他 11.5%。蘋果營收主要來自中國和日本。根據蘋果說法，由於中國的蘋果營收高度以 iPhone 為主，而iPhone 12 的上市日從第三季延後到第四季，導致延後的銷售反映到第四季的營收。加上其他國家的 5G 發展速度較慢，對於 5G iPhone 的需求還沒出現爆發性的成長，中國5G 環境相對成熟，所以消費者可能延遲消費等到5G iPhone 推出，這也導致中國市場的明顯成長。<br />\n<br />\n各產品線：iPhone 營收YoY成長率達17.23%。由於iPhone 12 延遲到第四季上市，導致蘋果第三季 iPhone 營收下滑 20.7%。把第三季第四季的 iPhone 營收合併計算，2019 年下半年 iPhone 總營收為 893.4 億美元，而 2020 年下半年的 iPhone 總營收為 920.4 億美元，年成長率只有3%。<br />\n<br />\nMac 營收YoY 成長率達21.26%，成長幅度比Q3的29.2低。考慮到M1 Mac 推出不久，M1 Mac 能否有效幫助蘋果攻佔PC 市場仍需時間觀察。蘋果認為 M1 Mac 的轉換週期為兩年，意味兩年後大多數的 Mac 用戶都會轉移到M1 Mac。<br />\n<br />\n後面唔得閒寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\niPad 非常好<br />\n<br />\nwearable devices唔錯<br />\n<br />\n服務唔錯，但 apple tv+ 同 Arcade 垃圾"},{"pid":"6f509fc0759a04c31df001161a988fe4c9a6c342","tid":2394673,"uid":291526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"而家財報已經唔反應股價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79b16fff8a3fe0ea545f68eaf4ae27e33107676","tid":2394673,"uid":365423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"開咗sem好忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f0677f6d3f614e884f23d00dc4fe425e1a70a1","tid":2394673,"uid":316294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"135買<br />\n兩個月之後都係135 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0b29a0fb8b0f6c4fce13a8ecad3c4c7cf02ec0","tid":2394673,"uid":65658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 財報幾靚 都係跌"},{"pid":"54598a7f8ec22c41cd4539ae9ddde6af941c9911","tid":2394673,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"買TSLA啦<br />\n唔好再對AAPL抱有任何期望<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff53f288377877ee6045b39309a1b68c2b30030c","tid":2394673,"uid":205329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"股價已反應"},{"pid":"da61d62933cc191e283d04bc84ad6a552c582014","tid":2394673,"uid":57186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"19f0677f6d3f614e884f23d00dc4fe425e1a70a1","tid":2394673,"uid":316294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"135買<br />\n兩個月之後都係135 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"你咪好，我半年前132買，而家仲係133<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52449397e59e574cd1a00df3663eeda52148de6f","tid":2394673,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da61d62933cc191e283d04bc84ad6a552c582014","tid":2394673,"uid":57186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"19f0677f6d3f614e884f23d00dc4fe425e1a70